<html><head><title>Exclusive Berserker Epic Riddle</title></head><body class="newsbody" ><div class=newbody><h2>EverQuest Vault -- EQ </h3><h3>Exclusive Berserker Epic Riddle</h3><p>Today we have a riddle from SOE that relates to the Berserker Epic in the upcoming expansion, Omens of War:<blockquote><br>I'll burn without fire and leave not ash. <br>I'll fester and churn until the time that I pass.<br>I bring strength to your weapons and red to your face,<br>Until the thing that made is put in its place. <br></blockquote><br>If you think you know the answer to this riddle go ahead and click "Post a comment" up top and reply with what you think!  Tomorrow i'll be posting the answer and Friday we will have an exclusive piece of artwork for the Berserker Epic.</div><p><div classs=copyright><font face=arial size=2 color=#959595>News Story from EverQuest Vault -- EQ <br>News Date: Wed 18 Aug 2004<br>Link: http://eqvault.ign.com//index.php#773<br>Printed On: Tue Dec 21 16:45:12 PST 2004<br>©2004 IGN Entertainment</font></span>